## Third-Party Components

This repository includes setup scripts for third-party tools:

### prc-tools
- License: GNU General Public License (GPL)
- Project: https://github.com/savaughn/prc-tools-remix
- Pre-built binaries: https://github.com/savaughn/prc-tools-remix/releases/tag/macos-arm

### Palm OS SDK
- License: Palm OS License Agreement
- Project: https://github.com/jichu4n/palm-os-sdk
- Usage: Educational and non-commercial development

### pilrc
- License: GNU General Public License (GPL)
- Installed via: Homebrew (jichu4n/palm-os tap)

### pilot-link
- License: GNU General Public License (GPL)
- Installed via: Homebrew

